Package: circus
Type: Package
Title: Helper functions to wrangle animal 'brmsfit' models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Fonti Kar
Maintainer: Fonti Kar <fonti.kar@gmail.com>
Description: circus is a package for wrangling and summarising 'brmsfit' mixed model objects. The package allows quick calculations of intra-class correlations (ICC) coefficients such as heritability from 'animal' models
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    brms,
    MCMCglmm
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
